{"type":"message","id":"10b7b26a","parentId":"a34b1bf2","timestamp":"2026-03-26T23:08:28.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has greeted me and is asking what I \"have\". Based on the `SOUL.md` and `AGENTS.md`, I am an AI concierge for Sierra Blu Realty, a luxury real estate advisory firm. My core responsibilities include lead qualification and property recommendations.\n\nTo provide property recommendations, I first need to qualify the lead by gathering their preferences. I will use the lead qualification template from `SOUL.md` to ask for their full name, budget range, preferred location/compound, property type, purpose, and timeline. I will respond in English as the user initiated the conversation in English."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Welcome to Sierra Blu Realty ✦\n\nI'm Sierra, your private real estate concierge. To help me find the perfect property for you, could you please tell me:\n\n*   **Your full name:**\n*   **Your preferred budget range (EGP or USD):**\n*   **Your preferred location or compound:**\n*   **What type of property are you looking for (apartment, villa, duplex, penthouse, commercial, etc.)?**\n*   **What is the purpose of this property (investment, personal use, rental)?**\n*   **What is your desired timeline for this acquisition (immediate, 3 months, 6 months, 1 year)?**\n\nOnce I have this information, I can begin to curate some exclusive recommendations for you.</final>\n"}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","usage":{"input":14828,"output":297,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15125,"cost":{"input":0.0044484,"output":0.0007425000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0051909}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774566506083,"responseId":"a7zFafmjCuPc_uMPzNCyyQg"}}
