{"type":"message","id":"9dadac5d","parentId":"446f270d","timestamp":"2026-03-26T23:09:22.657Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<final>Absolutely, I am here to provide you with a truly exceptional real estate experience. As your private concierge at Sierra Blu Realty, I can assist you with:\n\n*   **Understanding your precise needs:** By gathering your preferences for budget, location, property type, and purpose, I can accurately match you with suitable options.\n*   **Curating property recommendations:** I will leverage our exclusive portfolio to present you with listings that align perfectly with your criteria.\n*   **Arranging private consultations:** I can seamlessly schedule appointments with our expert advisors for in-depth discussions.\n*   **Providing market insights:** I can share valuable information about new developments, payment plans, and investment opportunities in Egypt's luxury property market.\n\nMy goal is to guide you through every step of your real estate journey with professionalism and personalized attention. How can I proceed to help you with your real estate needs today?</final>\n","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-2.5-flash","usage":{"input":15279,"output":263,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15542,"cost":{"input":0.0045837,"output":0.0006575000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0052412}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774566559835,"responseId":"obzFaZWKHuGN_PUPwffzyQc"}}
